{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore\/samSelectDetailRegion","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"preciseIdentifier":"c:I","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"samSelectDetailRegion"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@sam_color_image","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore\/sam_color_image","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SamColorImage"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"image"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"const"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:I","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"detectedObjectBoundingBox"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:I","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"int"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"selectedBoundingBox"},{"kind":"text","text":");"}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Return Value","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"return-value"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0 on success, or a non-zero error code on failure."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Analyzes the input image and identifies the most suitable 200x200 pixel"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"region (bounding box) with high level of details that intersects a given bounding box."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox"},{"type":"text","text":" is empty (width or height is 0), any region can be selected. Otherwise,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the selected region should have non-empty intersection with this bounding box. The selected region"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"should lie fully inside the input image."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If there is no region satisfying these conditions - if image width or height is smaller than 200"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"detectedObjectBoundingBox"},{"type":"text","text":" lies outside the image, the selected bounding box will be (0, 0, 200, 200)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["                                  a bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height)."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null},{"code":["                                  return, contains the bounding box in the format (x, y, width, height),","                                  where width and height are always set to 200."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"title":"samSelectDetailRegion","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"DotFaceCore"}],"roleHeading":"Function","symbolKind":"func","fragments":[{"text":"samSelectDetailRegion","kind":"identifier"}],"externalID":"c:@F@samSelectDetailRegion"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/dotfacecore\/samselectdetailregion"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://DotFaceCore/documentation/DotFaceCore":{"abstract":[{"text":"version: 9.4.1","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/dotfacecore","title":"DotFaceCore","identifier":"doc:\/\/DotFaceCore\/documentation\/DotFaceCore","role":"collection"},"doc://DotFaceCore/documentation/DotFaceCore/sam_color_image":{"url":"\/documentation\/dotfacecore\/sam_color_image","fragments":[{"text":"sam_colo